These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  police-officer, dancer, bartender, teacher, nurse, project-manager, engineer
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, polish, dutch, japanese, indian, spanish
 1. the teacher is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the japanese is the teacher##1
 3. the engineer is on the right of the project-manager##1
 4. the polish is on the right of the indian##1
 5. the bartender is in the middle##1
 6. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 7. the nurse is the egyptian##1
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the indian##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the indonesian##1
10. the dutch is on the left of the bartender##1
11. the engineer is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | nurse | teacher | dancer | bartender | police-officer | project-manager | engineer |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | japanese   | dutch      | indian | polish    | indonesian    | spanish         |

