.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: orange, garlic, lettuce, pepper, cherry, blueberry, spinach
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, electronic, hip-hop, techno, reggae, dubstep
 1. the fan of techno is the person eating pepper##1
 2. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
 3. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating garlic is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the fan of techno is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
10. the person eating pepper is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | orange | garlic | cherry | pepper | blueberry | spinach | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | electronic   | hip-hop   | techno      | ambient       | dubstep       | reggae     |

