.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: tomato, broccoli, cranberry, pineapple, grapefruit, garlic, mango
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, accountant, designer, musician, doctor, journalist, dressmaker
 1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 3. the accountant is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 4. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 5. the dancer is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the accountant##1
 7. the accountant is on the left of the designer##1
 8. the accountant is on the right of the musician##1
 9. the person eating garlic is the musician##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the musician is in the middle##1
12. the person eating mango is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | broccoli | grapefruit     | cranberry  | garlic       | tomato       | mango  | pineapple   |
| Job    | journalist  | dancer | dressmaker | musician | accountant | designer | doctor |

