.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: punk, d&b, electronic, reggae, country, salsa, blues
There are 7 different nationalities: american, polish, chinese, malaysian, dutch, mexican, japanese
 1. the fan of country is the polish##1
 2. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the mexican is on the right of the chinese##1
 4. the american is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 7. the chinese is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the right of the mexican##1
 9. the fan of electronic is the dutch##1
10. the dutch is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
11. the japanese is the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | blues     | reggae     | electronic      | d&b | country      | punk     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | chinese | mexican | dutch | japanese | polish | american |

