.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, puzzles, skydiving, hiking, filmmaking, hedgehoging, chess
7 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog, lizard, rat, cat, mouse, hamster
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is hedgehoging##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | skydiving | hedgehoging     | hiking | chess | filmmaking | woodworking |
| Pet     | hamster   | lizard    | cat | mouse     | pony         | rat     | hedgehog        |

