.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, cola, fanta, lemonade, water, milk
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, subway, boat, helicopter, van, train, motorbike
 1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | cola | water   | tea | fanta | milk  | lemonade | mirinda |
| Transport   | helicopter   | van | taxi | train     | subway | motorbike | boat   |

