.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, action, superhero, western, spy, musical, horror
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, van, bike, subway, helicopter, tram, taxi
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the car is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | horror | western | spy | musical     | action | superhero |
| Transport     | tram | subway      | taxi | bike    | helicopter | van   | car  |

