 4. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby       | drawing   | video-games | reading | photography | traveling     | collecting | hiking |
| Transport   | tram | bus      | motorbike        | trike         | airplane | skateboard     | subway |

